data.description: **Ideal Location!** This end unit townhome, just 3.3 miles from Red Hat Amphitheater and Downtown Raleigh, offers convenience and charm. Highlights include new paint throughout, hardwood floors downstairs, brand new carpet upstairs, upper-level owner suite, attached garage, gas log fireplace, granite counters, stainless steel appliances and much more. With a cozy atmosphere and modern amenities, this townhome is a must-see!
